                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190526-47-off251 t18190526-47-cd252"></join>, 41 lbs. of lead, value 8 s. 6 d., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18190526-47-victim485" type="victimName">
