                     <interp inst="t18190526-47-person489" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prisoner running - he threw the lead away.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18190526-47-person490">
                  JOHN 
                  BLUE
               <interp inst="t18190526-47-person490" type="surname" value="BLUE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190526-47-person490" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190526-47-person490" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a plumber. I had laid the gutters down only a week before; I compared the lead with the roof, and it fitted exactly. It weighs 41 lbs.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I went there to look for work, and picked the lead up in the house; I saw nobody there, and left.</p>
